ActCustoms Tariff
Subject13th IAAF World Junior Championships in Athletics Remission Order, 2010
Precis13th IAAF WORLD JUNIOR CHAMPIONSHIPS IN ATHLETICS REMISSION ORDER, 2010, which remits customs duties and all or a portion of the goods and services tax or harmonized sales tax paid or payable on items such as personal effects, goods for free distribution, display goods and equipment imported into Canada in connection with the 13th Championships to be held in Moncton, New Brunswick from July 19 to 25, 2010.
